      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Wiꞥſch darrija arridsan\ntahs wiſsfwehttakas Weetas\nNammu / tas bija diwidefmits\nOhlektis garfch/ un diwidefmits\nOhlektis plats/ un wiꞥſch pahr-\nwilke to ar labbu Seltu pee jeſch-\njints Talenteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Un to Naglu Swars bija\npee peezdefmits Sihkteem Sel-\nta/ un pahrwilke tahs angstas\nIstabas ar Seltu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Wiꞥſch darrija arridsan\ntai wiſsfwehttakas Weetas Nam-\nma divi Kerubim Bidneeku\nDarba/ un pahrwilke tohs ar\ndehtm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "11. Un to Kerubu Spahrni\nbija diwidefmits Ohlefschu Gar-\nyuma/ weens Spahrns bija no\npezahm Ohlektin/ un fneedse\nlihds ta Namma Seenam/ un\ntas ohtrs Spahrns bija arridsan\nno peezahm Ohlektim/ un fneedse\nlihds ta ohtra Keruba Spahr-\nnam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "12. Ta patt bija arridsan ta\n"
    },
