    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "13. Scho Kerubu Spa-\nisplehtahs diwidefmits Ohlekt\nan tee stahweja uß fanahm K\njahm/ un winnu Waigi bija\nEekschpufti greestii.\n"
