      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Wiꞥſch darrija arrid-\nSchkehdes ka Deewa Ru-\nfchanas Weeta/ un likke tahs\nto Stabbu Bohgahin : V\ndarrija wiꞥſch finits Grana-\nun likke tohs starp tahm Sch-\n"
